the release dry-run publish tree. Do not publish by zipping or copying the raw
working directory: ignored local material such as `.build/`, Xcode user data,
local FastVLM sources, local model bundles, and local signing/project overrides
is intentionally outside the source release boundary.

The source release notice policy accepts structured third-party inventories
alongside the applicable top-level license/provenance files named below. If a
downstream distribution policy requires complete per-package license texts,
generate and review that expanded notice set before distributing the derived
artifact.

