```

The bundled browser/runtime assets include `chat-unified-markdown.js`, which
bundles unified/remark/rehype/micromark, MathJax (`mathjax-full`), KaTeX,
mhchemparser, and related browser markdown packages, plus standalone KaTeX,
highlight.js, Prettier, d3, markmap-view, and pagedjs resources. Their license
